## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="81f62-212">O exemplo a seguir define um manipulador de eventos que coleta informações sobre um <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioSignalProblemOccurred> eventos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="81f62-212">The following example defines an event handler that gathers information about an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioSignalProblemOccurred> event.</span></span>  

