## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="81f62-638">O exemplo a seguir obtém uma lista parcial de dados para o mecanismo de reconhecimento de fala no processo atual.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="81f62-638">The following example gets a partial list of data for the current in-process speech recognition engine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="81f62-639">Para obter mais informações, consulte <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="81f62-639">For more information, see <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>.</span></span>  

